element_text(size = 8, hjust = 1), plot.margin = margin(25,25,25,25), legend.direction = "horizontal", legend.background = element_rect(fill = "papayawhip"), legend.title = element_blank(), legend.key.size = unit(0.5, "cm"), legend.position = c(0.70, 0.90) )ggsave(plot = last_plot(), filename = here::here("output", "4.pdf"), dpi = 300, height = 10, width = 10)Original: Eliane Mitchell
